title: White House says Trump 'won' dispute with porn star
text:
White House says Trump 'won' dispute with porn star 7:34pm EST - 02:13 
The White House on Wednesday dismissed a lawsuit against the president by adult film star Stormy Daniels, claiming the case had gone to arbitration, which Donald Trump 'won.'
